task.summary: Default task
Tests for Row classes. Added method to ReviewerDb to reconstruct review from table given Id. Still need to write test for it.
Test for getReviewFromDb in ReviewerDb. Seems to work. Added equals and hashcode to MdDataList.
Added getReviewTree method to ReviewerDb. Not tested yet.
Adjusted getReviewTree in ReviewerDb in light of tests. Tests now pass. Add ReviewTreeComparer to help compare equality between nodes and between trees. Add getRoot() to ReviewNode interface.
Added database cache to the app. Saves on publishing. Loads published reviews on app start.

Added method for deleting review trees from DB. Added method for loading tags from DB into TagsManager. Changed TagsManager to take ReviewIds rather than Reviewes themselves as args to facilitate this.
Fixed some tests in light of yesterday's changes
Added loadTags test to ReviewerDbTest
testAddMultipleTrees added to ReviewerDbTest
Added testAddMultipleTrees and testDeleteReviewTreeFromDb to ReviewerDbTest
Added option to delete published review from feed screen using long click
Fixed an inadvertant bug
Fixed an inadvertant bug
Started adding UI for consuming reviews using a tree system of ReviewViewAdapters using ReviewDataAdapter. Not quite working yet...
Started adding UI for consuming reviews using a tree system of ReviewViewAdapters using ReviewDataAdapter. Kind of working.
Fixed Controller tests in light of recent changes
Fixed tests in light of recent changes
Added copy constructors to GvDataLists and GvDatas. MdGvConverter now refers to these.
In the process of adding a test database filled with data to test against
Added tests for TestDatabase. Changed the way ReviewBuilder makes trees for publication. There was too much unnecessary wrappping going on. Administrator can load test database if required.
Fixed a few bugs, cleaned up some code.
Updated Controller package tests in light of recent changes
Updated Database package tests in light of recent changes
Some test changes
Went through all tests in light of recent activity and adjusted accordingly.
Tests for ReviewFeedAdapter, ReviewNodeAdapter, ReviewDataAdapter.
Split out feed stuff from Administrator into separate ReviewFeed class. Add getInternalNode() back to reviews as think it will help navigating and expanding review trees.

Split out getGridData() and expandItem() from some of the ReviewViewAdapters and moved them to separate GridDataWrapper and GridDataExpander classes. ReviewViewBasic uses these to help generalise the adapters to make them more flexible.
Tests for the various expanders and wrappers
In the process of writing adapters for consuming reviews, e.g. aggregate adapter for viewing feed as a meta rreview etc.
Some code cleanup to help integrate the Launchable pattern for constructing screens for consuming reviews
Got aggregate view of feed working
Some code cleanup
Adjusted some tests in COntroller in light of recent changes
Added a bunch of tests for stuff in Reviewer->Model
Changed ReviewId to construct ids out of Author's UserId and time of construction in milliseconds.
Fixed a bug in ReviewView that wasn't returning mGridViewData.
Some code cleanup
Some code cleanup
Introduced more granular packages to help organise code base
Introduced more granular packages to help organise code base - tests
Introduced more granular packages to help organise code base - tests
Chnaged Controller package name to Adapter
In the rocess of clarifying how to travel down trees and into nodes...
In the process of clarifying how to travel down trees and into nodes. Still.
In the process of clarifying how to travel down trees and into nodes. ViewerTreeData has collectCriteria now instead of using a criteria collector.
Got basic viewing of GvData at end of expander chain to work. Currently just using edit dialog to see if it works.
Got basic viewing of GvData at end of expander chain to work. Using ViewChildReview for child reviews.
